Text: Golf TournyMark Greetings Im glad to hear that you might make it to the Steve Couch Memorial Golf Tournament this Friday If you want to play we have a place for you We will either put you with a team that needs a fourth or simply put you on a foursome if other teams are filled I know that Brad Schick is in the same boat that your are so Im looking for a team for him also Whatever we do we will find a place for you I hope you can get off work and join us Please let me know if Dials team needs you or you find a spot on another team I look forward to seeing you Friday Donnie PS If you need to get in touch with me during the day you can email me at work at mailto This note is coming from my home email address
